          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="text-xl sm:text-2xl font-bold text-[#010101] mb-2 sm:mb-3">Multiplataforma</h3>
        <p class="text-[#010101]/70 leading-relaxed text-sm sm:text-base mb-6">
          Accede desde PC, tablet o celular. Tu negocio en la palma de tu mano, donde sea que estés.
        </p>
        <div class="flex justify-center mt-auto">
          <img src="/multiplataforma.png" alt="Ilustración Multiplataforma" class="w-full max-w-[240px] h-auto object-contain" />
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Benefit 5 -->
      <div class="benefit-card scroll-reveal group p-6 sm:p-8 rounded-2xl border-2 border-gray-100 hover:border-[#3E37FC] hover:shadow-[0_10px_40px_rgba(62,55,252,0.2)] transition-all duration-500 hover:-translate-y-2 cursor-pointer">
        <div class="w-12 h-12 sm:w-14 sm:h-14 bg-[#3E37FC]/10 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center mb-4 sm:mb-6 group-hover:bg-gradient-to-br group-hover:from-[#3E37FC] group-hover:to-[#2B25B8] transition-all duration-500 shadow-[0_4px_15px_rgba(62,55,252,0.15)] group-hover:scale-110 group-hover:rotate-12">
          <svg class="w-7 h-7 sm:w-8 sm:h-8 text-[#3E37FC] group-hover:text-white transition-colors duration-300" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M18.364 5.636l-3.536 3.536m0 5.656l3.536 3.536M9.172 9.172L5.636 5.636m3.536 9.192l-3.536 3.536M21 12a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0zm-5 0a4 4 0 11-8 0 4 4 0 018 0z"></path>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="text-xl sm:text-2xl font-bold text-[#010101] mb-2 sm:mb-3">Soporte</h3>
        <p class="text-[#010101]/70 leading-relaxed text-sm sm:text-base mb-6">
          Atención y asistencia técnica cuando lo necesites. Estamos aquí para ayudarte a resolver cualquier duda.
        </p>
        <div class="flex justify-center mt-auto">
          <img src="/soporte.png" alt="Ilustración Soporte" class="w-full max-w-[240px] h-auto object-contain" />
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Benefit 6 -->
      <div class="benefit-card scroll-reveal group p-6 sm:p-8 rounded-2xl border-2 border-gray-100 hover:border-[#3E37FC] hover:shadow-[0_10px_40px_rgba(62,55,252,0.2)] transition-all duration-500 hover:-translate-y-2 cursor-pointer">
        <div class="w-12 h-12 sm:w-14 sm:h-14 bg-[#3E37FC]/10 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center mb-4 sm:mb-6 group-hover:bg-gradient-to-br group-hover:from-[#3E37FC] group-hover:to-[#2B25B8] transition-all duration-500 shadow-[0_4px_15px_rgba(62,55,252,0.15)] group-hover:scale-110 group-hover:rotate-12">
          <svg class="w-7 h-7 sm:w-8 sm:h-8 text-[#3E37FC] group-hover:text-white transition-colors duration-300" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 19v-6a2 2 0 00-2-2H5a2 2 0 00-2 2v6a2 2 0 002 2h2a2 2 0 002-2zm0 0V9a2 2 0 012-2h2a2 2 0 012 2v10m-6 0a2 2 0 002 2h2a2 2 0 002-2m0 0V5a2 2 0 012-2h2a2 2 0 012 2v14a2 2 0 01-2 2h-2a2 2 0 01-2-2z"></path>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="text-xl sm:text-2xl font-bold text-[#010101] mb-2 sm:mb-3">Reportes en Tiempo Real</h3>
        <p class="text-[#010101]/70 leading-relaxed text-sm sm:text-base mb-6">
          Visualiza el estado de tu negocio al instante. Dashboards y reportes actualizados en tiempo real.
        </p>
        <div class="flex justify-center mt-auto">
          <img src="/reportes.png" alt="Ilustración Reportes en Tiempo Real" class="w-full max-w-[240px] h-auto object-contain" />
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

